WEBVTT

00:01:33.330 --> 00:01:34.800
[OVERDO]

00:01:35.300 --> 00:01:37.750
[Episode 5]

00:01:40.670 --> 00:01:45.900
[Murong Residence]

00:01:54.509 --> 00:01:55.070
Qingyu.

00:01:56.280 --> 00:01:57.430
Rest assured, Qingyu.

00:01:57.430 --> 00:01:58.640
When the aviation school opens,

00:01:58.640 --> 00:02:00.040
Whether my father shows up or not,

00:02:00.040 --> 00:02:00.900
I will be there.

00:02:01.430 --> 00:02:02.230
Thank you.

00:02:02.760 --> 00:02:03.790
If it puts you in a bind...

00:02:03.790 --> 00:02:05.480
"Bear family burdens without complaint;

00:02:05.480 --> 00:02:07.230
Transcend self-interest in the clan."

00:02:07.230 --> 00:02:08.870
You taught me this since I was little.

00:02:08.870 --> 00:02:10.000
Have you forgotten?

00:02:10.800 --> 00:02:11.310
Ali.

00:02:12.080 --> 00:02:13.280
What's the deal tonight?

00:02:13.280 --> 00:02:14.310
It's so secretive.

00:02:14.310 --> 00:02:15.680
We couldn't even drive in.

00:02:15.680 --> 00:02:16.360
Young Master,

00:02:16.360 --> 00:02:17.310
Please head in

00:02:17.310 --> 00:02:18.510
And see for yourself.

00:02:18.910 --> 00:02:19.710
Interesting.

00:02:19.800 --> 00:02:21.329
Even Boze is out of the loop.

00:02:23.280 --> 00:02:24.210
Today's banquet

00:02:24.280 --> 00:02:25.710
Was arranged by Mulan.

00:02:26.000 --> 00:02:27.660
She decorated the courtyard.

00:02:28.520 --> 00:02:30.630
Then I'll be sure to take a good look.

00:02:34.000 --> 00:02:35.200
Do you recognize him?

00:02:37.030 --> 00:02:38.290
Your Young Master Huo.

00:02:39.750 --> 00:02:41.610
My master's hosting this banquet

00:02:41.680 --> 00:02:43.480
Just to let you catch up with him.

00:02:44.310 --> 00:02:46.150
I left the Huo household a long time ago.

00:02:46.150 --> 00:02:47.870
I've been honestly looking for work

00:02:47.870 --> 00:02:48.910
To make a living.

00:02:49.120 --> 00:02:50.360
Why must your master do this...

00:02:50.360 --> 00:02:52.560
You did so many dirty deeds for the Huos.

00:02:53.000 --> 00:02:54.800
Do you think your hands are clean

00:02:55.360 --> 00:02:57.490
Just after 2 years as a lawful citizen?

00:02:58.310 --> 00:02:59.040
Don't worry.

00:03:00.000 --> 00:03:00.960
For your sins,

00:03:00.960 --> 00:03:02.750
The victims will naturally come for you.

00:03:02.750 --> 00:03:04.560
My master isn't that nosy.

00:03:05.310 --> 00:03:06.970
He's just giving you a choice.

00:03:07.360 --> 00:03:08.560
You're over 50 now, and still

00:03:08.560 --> 00:03:10.420
Running around looking for work.

00:03:10.430 --> 00:03:11.430
It must be tough.

00:03:12.590 --> 00:03:14.650
Later at the banquet, you just need to

00:03:14.870 --> 00:03:16.930
Identify the murderer for my master.

00:03:17.150 --> 00:03:18.430
Then, for the rest of your life,

00:03:18.430 --> 00:03:20.030
You'll be well provided for.

00:03:44.120 --> 00:03:46.320
Didn't they say cars aren't allowed in?

00:03:47.800 --> 00:03:48.470
Laiyi.

00:03:49.079 --> 00:03:50.280
Young Master Qingyu.

00:03:51.280 --> 00:03:52.030
Who is this?

00:03:55.190 --> 00:03:56.310
You are...

00:03:57.400 --> 00:03:58.800
Hello, Young Master Zongqi.

00:03:58.800 --> 00:04:01.400
I'm Li Cai, the butler of Yu Estate in Beicheng.

00:04:32.510 --> 00:04:33.310
He's here.

00:04:37.159 --> 00:04:38.290
What about the Huos?

00:04:39.510 --> 00:04:41.570
He recognized Huo Zongqi at the door.

00:04:42.360 --> 00:04:44.420
I haven't mentioned Miss Fang to him.

00:04:48.240 --> 00:04:49.000
Okay.

00:04:50.120 --> 00:04:52.120
Let's leave a surprise for the Huos.

00:04:55.190 --> 00:04:57.650
If that butler really recognizes Miss Fang,

00:04:57.920 --> 00:04:59.720
The Huos will probably kill her.

00:05:02.560 --> 00:05:04.160
Have you thought it through?

00:05:18.560 --> 00:05:19.690
Help me tie my apron.

00:05:20.600 --> 00:05:21.120
Coming.

00:06:36.020 --> 00:06:38.050
♪ Fantasies reduced to ash ♪

00:06:37.190 --> 00:06:37.870
Hold still.

00:06:38.130 --> 00:06:40.020
♪ In a raging fire ♪

00:06:43.159 --> 00:06:44.000
Keep staring,

00:06:43.700 --> 00:06:45.870
♪ Those caught in the wake ♪

00:06:44.270 --> 00:06:45.920
And I'll gouge your eyes out.

00:06:45.900 --> 00:06:47.840
♪ Now tell only gray lies ♪

00:06:51.490 --> 00:06:53.040
♪ Willingly ♪

00:06:53.070 --> 00:06:54.980
♪ Surrendering the naive visage ♪

00:06:54.750 --> 00:06:56.720
Butler Li is waiting outside.

00:06:56.300 --> 00:06:58.170
♪ Of the past ♪

00:06:58.360 --> 00:06:59.390
Still want to run?

00:07:02.090 --> 00:07:04.370
♪ With no expectation of dawn ♪

00:07:06.920 --> 00:07:08.190
Making such a big fuss

00:07:08.600 --> 00:07:10.530
And returning with a new identity,

00:07:10.750 --> 00:07:12.510
You must have an ulterior motive.

00:07:11.240 --> 00:07:13.800
♪ Wandering beneath a pitch-black sky ♪

00:07:13.870 --> 00:07:15.160
Since you have a motive,

00:07:13.870 --> 00:07:15.940
♪ I smell no sorrow ♪

00:07:15.430 --> 00:07:16.870
You must have helpers.

00:07:18.190 --> 00:07:19.600
Do you think I'm that stupid

00:07:19.540 --> 00:07:21.480
♪ Let the story start over ♪

00:07:20.120 --> 00:07:21.520
To not have a backup plan?

00:07:21.520 --> 00:07:23.740
♪ With a new beginning ♪

00:07:27.170 --> 00:07:29.410
♪ When our paths cross again ♪

00:07:27.920 --> 00:07:29.540
The banquet hasn't even started.

00:07:29.540 --> 00:07:31.330
♪ I shift my gaze away ♪

00:07:30.560 --> 00:07:32.220
How much have you had to drink?

00:07:32.630 --> 00:07:34.120
You're already blabbering nonsense.

00:07:34.080 --> 00:07:35.490
♪ Only then can I ♪

00:07:37.610 --> 00:07:39.750
♪ Rid all hope ♪

00:07:43.180 --> 00:07:45.320
♪ No longer able to break free ♪

00:07:43.560 --> 00:07:44.950
Death is at your door,

00:07:44.950 --> 00:07:46.300
Yet you still won't own up.

00:07:46.300 --> 00:07:49.780
♪ From the shackles of destiny ♪

00:07:51.120 --> 00:07:53.250
♪ No more questioning ♪

00:07:54.010 --> 00:07:56.850
♪ The cruel jests of fate ♪

00:07:58.780 --> 00:08:00.930
♪ Now I know to appreciate ♪

00:08:00.310 --> 00:08:01.000
Fine.

00:08:02.120 --> 00:08:03.430
Since you won't own up,

00:08:02.370 --> 00:08:04.650
♪ The calm as it shatters ♪

00:08:04.120 --> 00:08:05.920
Let the people from Yu Estate see

00:08:06.170 --> 00:08:09.060
♪ No longer craving ♪

00:08:06.390 --> 00:08:08.000
Who really killed Huo Mingxi

00:08:08.070 --> 00:08:09.070
Back then!

00:08:09.150 --> 00:08:13.090
♪ Absolution from the heavens ♪

00:08:14.680 --> 00:08:17.500
♪ No innocent yesterdays ♪

00:08:15.950 --> 00:08:17.010
What are you doing?

00:08:17.240 --> 00:08:18.000
Let go of me!

00:08:18.700 --> 00:08:21.860
♪ My intuition is my only faith ♪

00:08:20.270 --> 00:08:21.040
Let go of me!

00:08:22.620 --> 00:08:25.870
♪ Pull out all the stops to deliver ♪

00:08:25.890 --> 00:08:28.600
♪ A show-stopper ♪

00:08:27.510 --> 00:08:28.270
Let go of me!

00:08:28.750 --> 00:08:29.510
Let go!

00:08:36.000 --> 00:08:36.549
Jinrui.

00:08:38.390 --> 00:08:39.450
Boze, you're here!

00:08:39.600 --> 00:08:40.270
Come, come.

00:08:40.390 --> 00:08:41.240
Come over.

00:08:41.390 --> 00:08:42.390
A new dress?

00:08:42.870 --> 00:08:43.870
That's right.

00:08:44.120 --> 00:08:45.440
Don't I look pretty?

00:08:45.720 --> 00:08:46.450
Very pretty.

00:08:46.670 --> 00:08:48.080
You look 10 years younger.

00:08:48.080 --> 00:08:49.810
I thought you were a movie star.

00:08:50.510 --> 00:08:51.670
Oh, please.

00:08:51.870 --> 00:08:52.630
Naughty.

00:08:53.120 --> 00:08:54.270
Come on. Let's go

00:08:54.270 --> 00:08:55.120
Take a look over there.

00:08:55.120 --> 00:08:55.600
Sure.

00:09:01.270 --> 00:09:03.360
I never imagined the Murong residence

00:09:03.360 --> 00:09:05.960
To have an area that exudes such Nanyang charm.

00:09:08.720 --> 00:09:10.580
Your soon-to-be brother-in-law

00:09:10.790 --> 00:09:12.790
Really is hard to read.

00:09:17.120 --> 00:09:18.200
I've never gotten involved

00:09:18.200 --> 00:09:19.960
In business in Beicheng.

00:09:21.720 --> 00:09:22.910
This Butler Li was

00:09:23.390 --> 00:09:23.840
A servant

00:09:23.840 --> 00:09:25.700
To my wrongfully deceased uncle.

00:09:26.320 --> 00:09:27.790
He just looks familiar.

00:09:28.790 --> 00:09:29.720
I don't understand

00:09:29.720 --> 00:09:31.720
Why Qingyi invited him.

00:09:36.480 --> 00:09:37.360
Qingyu,

00:09:38.630 --> 00:09:40.090
Know anything about this?

00:09:40.840 --> 00:09:41.840
Qingyi has always

00:09:41.840 --> 00:09:43.120
Been unpredictable.

00:09:43.870 --> 00:09:44.840
But don't worry.

00:09:45.550 --> 00:09:47.280
He knows where to draw the line.

00:09:48.720 --> 00:09:50.920
He sure does know where to draw the line.

00:09:51.910 --> 00:09:53.030
Qingyi said he wants

00:09:53.030 --> 00:09:54.560
To give the Huos a surprise.

00:09:55.750 --> 00:09:56.870
Could it be related to

00:09:56.870 --> 00:09:58.330
That case from 3 years ago?

00:10:03.440 --> 00:10:06.270
It's rare for us to gather for Qingyu's happy occasion.

00:10:06.270 --> 00:10:08.000
Heaven forbid things get ugly.

00:10:08.630 --> 00:10:09.390
Don't worry.

00:10:10.080 --> 00:10:11.210
I believe in Qingyi.

00:10:11.360 --> 00:10:12.510
I have something to do.

00:10:12.510 --> 00:10:13.390
Excuse me.

00:10:26.720 --> 00:10:28.250
You're about to be exposed.

00:10:28.550 --> 00:10:29.480
Are you excited?

00:10:30.550 --> 00:10:32.610
Do you want to be taken away by the Huos

00:10:32.910 --> 00:10:36.040
And die from their unspeakable, disgusting methods...

00:10:36.750 --> 00:10:37.790
Or should I

00:10:37.960 --> 00:10:39.030
Mercifully

00:10:39.200 --> 00:10:40.330
Send you on your way?

00:10:45.000 --> 00:10:45.870
Say something!

00:10:49.910 --> 00:10:51.600
Since you think I must die,

00:10:53.600 --> 00:10:54.750
I have a gift for you

00:10:55.670 --> 00:10:56.790
In the drawer

00:10:58.030 --> 00:10:58.910
In my room.

00:11:12.720 --> 00:11:13.650
Stay right here.

00:11:23.750 --> 00:11:24.480
Fang Mulan!

00:11:25.270 --> 00:11:26.080
Come here!

00:11:44.120 --> 00:11:45.440
That lady

00:11:46.080 --> 00:11:47.670
Looks familiar.

00:11:58.550 --> 00:12:00.410
In the Huos' place in Beicheng...

00:12:16.670 --> 00:12:18.630
That is a gift exclusively for you.

00:12:22.360 --> 00:12:24.320
If I must die today,

00:12:26.550 --> 00:12:27.360
I hope it will

00:12:27.360 --> 00:12:28.910
Always accompany you.

00:12:31.240 --> 00:12:32.750
I hope it accounts for

00:12:33.870 --> 00:12:34.910
Those 3 years.

00:12:55.390 --> 00:12:57.190
I have just one question for you:

00:12:58.720 --> 00:12:59.550
Right now...

00:13:02.150 --> 00:13:03.480
In this second,

00:13:04.550 --> 00:13:05.840
You do like me...

00:13:08.000 --> 00:13:08.750
Don't you?

00:13:15.840 --> 00:13:16.790
She clearly...

00:13:18.630 --> 00:13:19.960
Remembers everything.

00:13:31.510 --> 00:13:32.390
Oh no!

00:13:32.510 --> 00:13:33.720
Miss Fang fell into the water!

00:13:33.720 --> 00:13:34.960
Somebody help!

00:13:52.720 --> 00:13:53.550
Help!

00:13:54.440 --> 00:13:55.600
Can anybody swim?

00:13:54.850 --> 00:13:56.030
♪ Must it take heartache ♪

00:13:56.110 --> 00:13:58.020
♪ To know my heart belongs to you? ♪

00:13:58.920 --> 00:14:00.960
♪ Hearts cold no more ♪

00:14:01.090 --> 00:14:02.570
♪ Is every sweet dream ♪

00:14:02.610 --> 00:14:04.610
♪ Destined to fade away? ♪

00:14:05.620 --> 00:14:07.320
♪ Don't let it end in smoke ♪

00:14:07.800 --> 00:14:09.440
♪ Take away everything I have ♪

00:14:09.470 --> 00:14:11.380
♪ Can you bear the weight of it all? ♪

00:14:12.000 --> 00:14:14.350
♪ I offer you my whole life ♪

00:14:14.390 --> 00:14:15.970
♪ In exchange for my everything ♪

00:14:15.440 --> 00:14:16.550
Miss Fang caught a cold

00:14:16.000 --> 00:14:17.990
♪ Will you finally be mine? ♪

00:14:16.550 --> 00:14:17.270
And has a slight fever.

00:14:17.270 --> 00:14:18.270
She just slipped.

00:14:18.510 --> 00:14:19.360
Don't worry. She's fine.

00:14:18.690 --> 00:14:20.900
♪ Give me love and hate ♪

00:14:19.600 --> 00:14:20.730
Nothing to see here.

00:14:21.030 --> 00:14:24.540
♪ Let the tears fall, let the blood spill ♪

00:14:24.560 --> 00:14:27.120
♪ Even through suffering, I'll never let go of your hand ♪

00:14:27.640 --> 00:14:30.900
♪ I can't break free, I can't escape ♪

00:14:30.930 --> 00:14:33.410
♪ This, too, can be called a lifetime together ♪

00:14:33.490 --> 00:14:34.690
♪ We ♪

00:14:35.540 --> 00:14:37.740
♪ Remain bound by fate until the end ♪

00:14:38.500 --> 00:14:43.190
♪ Forevermore ♪

00:14:55.060 --> 00:14:57.760
♪ Neither you nor I ♪

00:14:59.910 --> 00:15:01.440
You can't escape this time,

00:15:00.260 --> 00:15:02.280
♪ Can ever break free ♪

00:15:02.120 --> 00:15:03.270
Ren Susu.

00:15:18.000 --> 00:15:18.670
How are you?

00:15:19.030 --> 00:15:19.960
Feeling better?

00:15:20.080 --> 00:15:21.340
Need me to get a doctor?

00:15:21.720 --> 00:15:22.390
No need.

00:15:22.390 --> 00:15:23.450
I feel much better.

00:15:24.440 --> 00:15:25.390
I'll be leaving then.

00:15:25.390 --> 00:15:26.630
Get some rest.

00:16:12.120 --> 00:16:13.180
It's an emergency.

00:16:13.630 --> 00:16:15.230
Might be an internal injury.

00:16:15.720 --> 00:16:16.200
Okay.

00:16:16.360 --> 00:16:18.490
I'll come to you as soon as possible...

00:16:20.030 --> 00:16:21.960
Trying to run after being exposed?

00:16:25.750 --> 00:16:27.670
Contacting your accomplice, huh?

00:16:27.670 --> 00:16:28.200
Go ahead.

00:16:32.600 --> 00:16:34.390
He's a famous doctor in the concession,

00:16:34.390 --> 00:16:36.910
Specializing in orthopedic rehabilitation.

00:16:36.910 --> 00:16:39.370
I was inviting him to take a look at your hand.

00:16:44.320 --> 00:16:45.380
It doesn't matter.

00:16:45.960 --> 00:16:48.020
My hand can't hold a scalpel anymore,

00:16:48.150 --> 00:16:50.210
But it's still very steady with a gun.

00:16:55.030 --> 00:16:55.870
Who did it?

00:16:57.870 --> 00:16:58.550
The Huos.

00:17:00.440 --> 00:17:01.870
They think Huo Mingxi's death

00:17:01.870 --> 00:17:03.200
Was orchestrated by me.

00:17:04.160 --> 00:17:05.589
So they hired someone to sever

00:17:05.589 --> 00:17:07.050
My hand tendons in prison.

00:17:07.589 --> 00:17:09.829
If the doctors in the concession can't fix it,

00:17:09.829 --> 00:17:10.960
I'll find one for you in Nanyang.

00:17:10.960 --> 00:17:12.420
I don't need your concern.

00:17:13.550 --> 00:17:15.030
I'm a surgeon.

00:17:15.310 --> 00:17:16.750
You think I can't tell if my hand

00:17:16.750 --> 00:17:17.810
Can be fixed or not?

00:17:26.880 --> 00:17:27.640
Qingyi.

00:17:30.720 --> 00:17:31.510
Be it the past

00:17:32.590 --> 00:17:33.590
Or the present...

00:17:36.480 --> 00:17:38.410
I've never thought of hurting you.

00:17:57.920 --> 00:17:58.450
Cover up.

00:18:27.110 --> 00:18:28.240
Why are you crying?

00:18:30.310 --> 00:18:31.440
Didn't you tell me

00:18:32.240 --> 00:18:33.770
You were only ever using me?

00:18:39.480 --> 00:18:40.880
Even if I'm disabled,

00:18:41.720 --> 00:18:43.350
What does it have to do with you?

00:18:43.350 --> 00:18:44.480
Whether I cry or not,

00:18:45.440 --> 00:18:47.170
What does it have to do with you?

00:18:53.510 --> 00:18:54.240
Forget it.

00:18:55.070 --> 00:18:57.070
If you truly feel guilty towards me,

00:18:57.440 --> 00:18:59.170
Then don't bring this up again.

00:19:08.270 --> 00:19:09.400
You still have

00:19:09.920 --> 00:19:11.120
That gentian flower.

00:19:12.750 --> 00:19:13.640
You lost it,

00:19:14.550 --> 00:19:15.480
And I found it.

00:19:15.590 --> 00:19:16.510
I didn't.

00:19:17.000 --> 00:19:18.160
On the train then...

00:19:25.350 --> 00:19:27.280
You clearly remember everything.

00:19:41.510 --> 00:19:43.000
You frown too much now.

00:19:46.030 --> 00:19:47.090
You didn't before.

00:19:51.510 --> 00:19:53.400
Anyone locked up in prison for 3 years

00:19:53.400 --> 00:19:55.070
Would forget their past self.

00:19:59.110 --> 00:19:59.830
I'm sorry.

00:20:12.000 --> 00:20:12.960
Ren Susu,

00:20:14.310 --> 00:20:15.370
Is a word of "sorry"

00:20:15.640 --> 00:20:17.040
The only thing you owe me?

00:20:20.550 --> 00:20:22.110
I detest your innocent act

00:20:22.110 --> 00:20:23.710
When you're full of schemes.

00:20:24.400 --> 00:20:26.000
If you really cared about me,

00:20:26.550 --> 00:20:27.680
How could you bear to

00:20:28.070 --> 00:20:30.330
Fake your death in front of me 3 years ago?

00:20:39.430 --> 00:20:41.160
♪ Sharper pain, deeper mark ♪

00:20:41.190 --> 00:20:43.240
♪ Deeper care, greater torment ♪

00:20:44.310 --> 00:20:46.110
If you want me to pay with my life,

00:20:46.100 --> 00:20:47.730
♪ I won't give up on you ♪

00:20:47.400 --> 00:20:48.790
You can do it now.

00:20:47.760 --> 00:20:49.950
♪ Don't let go of me ♪

00:20:51.970 --> 00:20:54.480
♪ Let the ropes of fate ♪

00:20:54.560 --> 00:20:57.360
♪ Bind you and me ♪

00:20:58.500 --> 00:21:00.890
♪ Even if led to a precipice ♪

00:21:00.980 --> 00:21:03.630
♪ Together, we fall ♪

00:21:05.310 --> 00:21:06.720
You're such a good actor.

00:21:05.800 --> 00:21:07.260
♪ In exchange for my everything ♪

00:21:07.290 --> 00:21:09.130
♪ Will you finally be mine? ♪

00:21:08.000 --> 00:21:09.660
You really think I won't do it?

00:21:10.050 --> 00:21:12.170
♪ Give me love and hate ♪

00:21:12.300 --> 00:21:15.800
♪ Let the tears fall, let the blood spill ♪

00:21:12.440 --> 00:21:13.840
You're always like this,

00:21:14.640 --> 00:21:16.200
Being soft-hearted at the critical moment.

00:21:15.830 --> 00:21:18.390
♪ Even through suffering, I'll never let go of your hand ♪

00:21:16.960 --> 00:21:18.490
That's why you always lose.

00:21:19.010 --> 00:21:22.160
♪ I can't break free, I can't escape ♪

00:21:22.200 --> 00:21:24.680
♪ This, too, can be called a lifetime together ♪

00:21:24.750 --> 00:21:25.960
♪ We ♪

00:21:27.010 --> 00:21:29.010
♪ Remain bound by fate until the end ♪

00:21:29.810 --> 00:21:34.460
♪ Forevermore ♪

00:21:46.440 --> 00:21:48.550
What do you plan to do about Butler Li?

00:22:01.000 --> 00:22:02.400
Let me warn you, Ren Susu.

00:22:02.880 --> 00:22:04.480
Behave and stay by my side.

00:22:05.160 --> 00:22:06.890
No more tricks and crazy ideas.

00:22:07.070 --> 00:22:08.670
It's your turn to experience

00:22:09.070 --> 00:22:10.640
What it's like to be manipulated.

00:22:10.640 --> 00:22:11.300
Otherwise,

00:22:12.510 --> 00:22:13.400
Butler Li can

00:22:14.440 --> 00:22:16.300
Pay a visit to the Huos at any time.

00:22:44.700 --> 00:22:50.130
[Huo Residence]

00:22:49.070 --> 00:22:50.000
Butler Li?

00:22:50.640 --> 00:22:52.590
Did you say Butler Li appeared at the Murong residence?

00:22:52.590 --> 00:22:53.240
Yes.

00:22:53.790 --> 00:22:55.120
I saw it with my own eyes.

00:22:55.510 --> 00:22:56.640
You bet it's real.

00:22:57.030 --> 00:22:59.310
What's Murong Qingyi up to again?

00:23:01.350 --> 00:23:03.080
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

00:23:03.110 --> 00:23:05.550
You chose not to attend the Murong banquet.

00:23:06.160 --> 00:23:07.720
Now you blame me?

00:23:16.400 --> 00:23:19.460
Butler Li's sudden appearance at the Murong residence

00:23:20.590 --> 00:23:22.880
Must be related to my father's death.

00:23:25.510 --> 00:23:27.550
You should've grabbed Murong Qingyi

00:23:27.550 --> 00:23:29.480
And interrogated him thoroughly.

00:23:47.400 --> 00:23:49.240
Such a pretty face...

00:23:51.240 --> 00:23:53.270
But such a stupid brain.

00:23:56.310 --> 00:23:57.970
Huo Minxian, keep in mind that

00:23:58.830 --> 00:24:01.960
You're just a loser from a collateral branch of the Huos.

00:24:02.070 --> 00:24:04.310
You have no right to yell at me.

00:24:07.590 --> 00:24:08.720
If you have the guts,

00:24:09.200 --> 00:24:10.350
Kill me.

00:24:11.750 --> 00:24:13.950
You can go marry Murong Qingyi instead.

00:24:16.400 --> 00:24:17.720
Do you still think your life

00:24:17.720 --> 00:24:19.000
Belongs to you?

00:24:24.830 --> 00:24:25.880
Believe it or not,

00:24:26.590 --> 00:24:28.790
I'll kill myself right in front of you.

00:24:33.000 --> 00:24:34.590
Go on. Do it.

00:24:35.550 --> 00:24:38.150
I'll make sure to take good care of your mother.

00:24:49.880 --> 00:24:51.310
Then at least tell me

00:24:52.160 --> 00:24:53.240
Where

00:24:54.790 --> 00:24:56.110
Butler Li is.

00:25:00.930 --> 00:25:04.570
[Taixing Hotel]

00:25:10.350 --> 00:25:11.010
Gentlemen,

00:25:11.030 --> 00:25:12.090
Please help me out.

00:25:12.790 --> 00:25:14.790
Young Master Qingyi didn't need me last night.

00:25:14.790 --> 00:25:17.110
I suppose I can't be of any help.

00:25:17.550 --> 00:25:19.720
Could you relay a message to him for me?

00:25:20.000 --> 00:25:21.440
Tell him I'm needed at home

00:25:21.440 --> 00:25:23.000
And to let me go back to Feng'an.

00:25:23.000 --> 00:25:23.830
Butler Li.

00:25:26.030 --> 00:25:27.030
Young Miss Minxian?

00:25:27.030 --> 00:25:28.360
Why are you in Nancheng?

00:25:29.200 --> 00:25:31.000
Did you go back to the main house?

00:25:32.550 --> 00:25:33.160
Miss Huo.

00:25:34.880 --> 00:25:35.640
Stopping me?

00:25:36.750 --> 00:25:38.720
I'm your master's fiancée.

00:25:39.000 --> 00:25:40.330
Are you tired of living?

00:25:44.440 --> 00:25:46.970
Did Murong Qingyi ask you to come to Nancheng?

00:25:47.030 --> 00:25:48.360
What did he ask you to do?

00:25:48.400 --> 00:25:50.270
He told me to identify someone.

00:25:50.960 --> 00:25:53.480
It seems to be related to what happened 3 years ago.

00:25:53.480 --> 00:25:55.080
Did you identify the person?

00:25:55.310 --> 00:25:56.960
Last night at the banquet,

00:25:57.200 --> 00:25:58.550
In the Murong residence,

00:25:58.550 --> 00:26:00.270
I did find a woman

00:26:00.510 --> 00:26:01.790
Familiar.

00:26:01.880 --> 00:26:04.340
Unfortunately, I didn't see her whole face.

00:26:08.720 --> 00:26:10.110
If you saw her again,

00:26:10.440 --> 00:26:11.840
Would you recognize her?

00:26:13.110 --> 00:26:13.840
Come with me.

00:26:14.310 --> 00:26:14.920
Miss Huo.

00:26:15.030 --> 00:26:15.830
No one can take him away

00:26:15.830 --> 00:26:17.960
Without Young Master Qingyi's order.

00:26:19.880 --> 00:26:21.000
I don't care.

00:26:21.510 --> 00:26:23.170
Let's see who dares to stop me.

00:26:33.790 --> 00:26:35.160
Notify Young Master Qingyi now.

00:26:35.160 --> 00:26:37.360
He went out of town for ancestral rites.

00:27:09.270 --> 00:27:13.390
[Spirit tablet of the late respected father, Murong Feng]

00:27:23.640 --> 00:27:24.970
Do you know how hard it is

00:27:25.310 --> 00:27:27.570
For me to be the pillar of the family alone

00:27:27.830 --> 00:27:28.750
With you gone?

00:27:31.680 --> 00:27:33.680
Fortunately, Qingyu is excellent.

00:27:33.790 --> 00:27:36.440
The Murong family will get stronger and stronger

00:27:36.440 --> 00:27:37.840
In my and Qingyu's hands.

00:27:40.070 --> 00:27:42.200
You can rest assured on the other side.

00:27:43.790 --> 00:27:45.550
Just wait for me to join you.

00:27:52.920 --> 00:27:53.510
Mother,

00:27:54.030 --> 00:27:55.270
Why isn't Boze here?

00:27:58.240 --> 00:28:00.170
He was just promoted to inspector.

00:28:00.720 --> 00:28:02.650
He's under close public scrutiny.

00:28:02.830 --> 00:28:04.880
Letting a descendant of Ying Army members

00:28:04.880 --> 00:28:06.720
Come to the Murong ancestral hall to

00:28:06.720 --> 00:28:08.640
Pay respects to Cheng Army members

00:28:08.640 --> 00:28:09.900
Would raise eyebrows.

00:28:12.070 --> 00:28:13.790
Mother, you're really thoughtful

00:28:13.790 --> 00:28:14.960
Of your dear son.

00:28:17.550 --> 00:28:18.110
Mother,

00:28:19.030 --> 00:28:20.430
We should let Father know

00:28:20.830 --> 00:28:22.270
About Mulan and me too.

00:28:30.720 --> 00:28:31.520
It's no hurry.

00:28:33.720 --> 00:28:34.750
Miss Fang,

00:28:35.000 --> 00:28:36.400
I'm afraid you don't know

00:28:36.480 --> 00:28:38.540
The background of our Murong family.

00:28:39.350 --> 00:28:40.030
Jinrui,

00:28:40.310 --> 00:28:41.510
As the eldest sister,

00:28:41.750 --> 00:28:43.070
Tell Miss Fang

00:28:43.440 --> 00:28:45.000
About our origins.

00:28:46.110 --> 00:28:47.110
Yes, Mother.

00:28:51.030 --> 00:28:52.110
Enshrined here are

00:28:52.110 --> 00:28:54.830
The spirit tablets of the Murong family.

00:28:53.010 --> 00:28:54.960
[Spirit tablet of the late respected father, Murong Feng]

00:28:55.000 --> 00:28:57.960
Our ancestors migrated to Songjiang at the end of the Yuan dynasty.

00:28:57.960 --> 00:29:00.920
With a history spanning several centuries...

00:29:02.720 --> 00:29:03.350
Miss Huo,

00:29:03.550 --> 00:29:04.480
Why are you here?

00:29:04.590 --> 00:29:05.920
Qingyi asked me to come.

00:29:06.030 --> 00:29:07.430
Go in and look carefully.

00:29:07.590 --> 00:29:09.000
If you see anyone suspicious,

00:29:09.000 --> 00:29:10.260
Point them out loudly.

00:29:10.310 --> 00:29:12.550
Young Miss, aren't you making things difficult for me?

00:29:12.550 --> 00:29:15.950
Everyone here, inside and out, is from the Murong household.

00:29:15.960 --> 00:29:17.000
Once you're sure,

00:29:17.400 --> 00:29:18.830
Go back to the main house

00:29:18.830 --> 00:29:20.000
To report it.

00:29:20.960 --> 00:29:22.030
Let the Old Master

00:29:22.030 --> 00:29:23.960
Punish the Murongs for their sins.

00:29:24.110 --> 00:29:24.790
Yes.

00:29:24.790 --> 00:29:27.790
Compared to some upstarts outside,

00:29:28.400 --> 00:29:30.800
Our "meritage" is naturally exceptional.

00:29:36.830 --> 00:29:38.350
What an illiterate.

00:29:38.790 --> 00:29:40.640
Mind you, it's "heritage."

00:29:40.750 --> 00:29:41.640
Your brain must

00:29:41.880 --> 00:29:44.240
Only be good for covering up for murderers.

00:29:44.240 --> 00:29:45.700
Did you just make fun of me?

00:29:45.880 --> 00:29:47.540
Miss Huo, you came uninvited.

00:29:47.750 --> 00:29:48.880
What is this about?

00:29:51.160 --> 00:29:52.310
Forgive me, Auntie.

00:29:52.310 --> 00:29:53.510
I was baffled when I heard

00:29:53.510 --> 00:29:55.000
That Qingyi is observing

00:29:55.750 --> 00:29:57.000
The ancestral rites,

00:29:57.440 --> 00:29:58.880
So I came to see the fun.

00:29:59.480 --> 00:30:02.140
Since when is a man who killed his father-in-law

00:30:02.590 --> 00:30:04.270
Qualified to

00:30:04.680 --> 00:30:07.030
Play the role of filial piety and loyalty?

00:30:08.680 --> 00:30:10.010
Have you lost your mind?

00:30:12.920 --> 00:30:14.000
Qingyi

00:30:14.110 --> 00:30:15.440
Brought my butler

00:30:15.550 --> 00:30:18.150
From Feng'an to Nancheng to identify someone.

00:30:19.590 --> 00:30:20.720
Who was identified?

00:30:21.160 --> 00:30:22.920
Don't you need to tell me?

00:30:23.310 --> 00:30:24.240
What butler?

00:30:24.640 --> 00:30:26.570
Why haven't I heard you mention it?

00:30:27.920 --> 00:30:29.240
Mother is asking you a question!

00:30:29.240 --> 00:30:32.570
-What are you doing behind our backs again? -Murong Qingyi.

00:30:32.960 --> 00:30:34.350
I now suspect that

00:30:34.920 --> 00:30:38.050
You're shielding your accomplice who killed my father.

00:30:38.270 --> 00:30:39.720
If you know what's good for you,

00:30:39.720 --> 00:30:41.000
Hand the person over.

00:30:44.030 --> 00:30:45.160
Where's your proof?

00:30:47.750 --> 00:30:48.550
Miss Huo,

00:30:49.350 --> 00:30:51.720
If you really can't bear to part with your paramour,

00:30:51.720 --> 00:30:53.380
Just call off the engagement.

00:30:54.030 --> 00:30:54.760
Oh, I forgot.

00:30:55.200 --> 00:30:56.920
Your paramour hasn't contacted you

00:30:56.920 --> 00:30:58.920
Since the theater incident, has he?

00:31:00.310 --> 00:31:02.200
I understand that you're upset,

00:31:02.880 --> 00:31:05.010
But this is the Murong ancestral hall.

00:31:05.480 --> 00:31:06.880
Isn't it ridiculous

00:31:07.270 --> 00:31:08.720
For you to make a scene here?

00:31:08.720 --> 00:31:10.180
Don't change the subject.

00:31:11.070 --> 00:31:12.350
I do like him.

00:31:12.640 --> 00:31:13.640
So what?

00:31:14.440 --> 00:31:16.000
Who do you think you are?

00:31:16.440 --> 00:31:18.510
They say you belong to two families,

00:31:19.030 --> 00:31:19.960
But really,

00:31:19.960 --> 00:31:22.560
You're just a loser that neither family wants.

00:31:22.680 --> 00:31:24.790
A dog unwanted by the Li family

00:31:24.920 --> 00:31:27.030
Scampered to the Murong family's door

00:31:27.030 --> 00:31:28.400
To beg for food,

00:31:28.680 --> 00:31:30.880
And now he's their second young master?

00:31:33.160 --> 00:31:34.920
You killed my father,

00:31:35.480 --> 00:31:37.310
Yet you expect me to marry you?

00:31:37.790 --> 00:31:38.720
On what grounds?

00:31:39.790 --> 00:31:42.440
On the grounds that you're a shameless,

00:31:42.680 --> 00:31:43.920
Ignorant, and scheming

00:31:43.920 --> 00:31:44.720
Murderer

00:31:44.720 --> 00:31:46.640
Who was abandoned by his parents?

00:31:59.960 --> 00:32:01.020
How dare you hit me?

00:32:01.790 --> 00:32:02.960
Disrespecting

00:32:03.350 --> 00:32:04.810
The ancestors and elders,

00:32:04.830 --> 00:32:07.270
Insulting your fiancé, and spreading rumors—

00:32:07.270 --> 00:32:09.800
Are these the manners your family taught you?

00:32:10.030 --> 00:32:11.290
Who are you to chime in?

00:32:11.920 --> 00:32:13.180
In terms of seniority,

00:32:13.240 --> 00:32:14.970
I'm your elder sister-in-law.

00:32:15.000 --> 00:32:16.060
In terms of status,

00:32:16.510 --> 00:32:19.030
I'm the daughter of the Fang family in Nanyang.

00:32:19.030 --> 00:32:20.090
It's not a matter of

00:32:20.240 --> 00:32:21.300
If I dare to hit you,

00:32:21.680 --> 00:32:22.960
But if I want to.

00:32:27.350 --> 00:32:29.240
Butler Li already recognized you.

00:32:29.240 --> 00:32:30.300
Aren't you afraid?

00:32:32.880 --> 00:32:33.640
With me here,

00:32:34.000 --> 00:32:34.930
Don't be afraid.

00:32:35.480 --> 00:32:36.240
With you here,

00:32:36.240 --> 00:32:37.500
I'm not afraid either.

00:32:43.920 --> 00:32:44.550
Miss Huo,

00:32:45.310 --> 00:32:46.960
Regarding your father's matter,

00:32:46.960 --> 00:32:48.240
Our two families already

00:32:48.240 --> 00:32:50.100
Reached a settlement 3 years ago.

00:32:50.550 --> 00:32:51.950
Qingyi has paid the price

00:32:52.110 --> 00:32:53.510
For his immaturity, too.

00:32:54.440 --> 00:32:55.070
Today,

00:32:56.640 --> 00:32:58.700
You came to the Murong ancestral hall

00:32:59.590 --> 00:33:01.400
And insulted members of my Murong family.

00:33:01.400 --> 00:33:02.640
If the Huo patriarch sent you,

00:33:02.640 --> 00:33:03.840
Then I'll consider it

00:33:04.200 --> 00:33:05.260
An act of hostility

00:33:05.550 --> 00:33:07.240
Towards my Murong family.

00:33:08.070 --> 00:33:09.110
Otherwise,

00:33:09.680 --> 00:33:11.280
You slandered my brother...

00:33:20.830 --> 00:33:21.920
I have a witness!

00:33:22.480 --> 00:33:24.680
Butler Li can prove who the murderer is!

00:33:28.270 --> 00:33:29.870
You finally remembered him.

00:33:30.070 --> 00:33:30.730
Where is he?

00:33:31.680 --> 00:33:32.750
Murong Qingyi,

00:33:33.240 --> 00:33:34.770
What did you do to Butler Li?

00:33:35.240 --> 00:33:36.750
Butler Li?

00:33:38.640 --> 00:33:40.170
Did any of you see Butler Li?

00:33:40.310 --> 00:33:40.970
-No. -No.

00:33:41.000 --> 00:33:41.590
No.

00:33:44.510 --> 00:33:45.200
You...

00:33:45.920 --> 00:33:47.270
Are you all blind?

00:33:48.310 --> 00:33:50.030
How can you allow this murderer

00:33:50.030 --> 00:33:52.030
To publicly take a witness hostage?

00:33:52.350 --> 00:33:53.880
When your father was alive,

00:33:54.000 --> 00:33:55.640
At least several dozen,

00:33:56.200 --> 00:33:57.400
If not a hundred, people

00:33:57.400 --> 00:33:58.860
Disappeared at his hands.

00:33:59.440 --> 00:34:01.100
Miss Huo, have you forgotten?

00:34:01.680 --> 00:34:02.550
So annoying.

00:34:03.160 --> 00:34:04.270
How do you want to disappear?

00:34:04.270 --> 00:34:05.070
I'll help you.

00:34:08.760 --> 00:34:09.360
Qingyi.

00:34:11.070 --> 00:34:11.630
Enough.

00:34:15.760 --> 00:34:16.510
Get lost.

00:34:29.840 --> 00:34:30.840
You unfilial son.

00:34:31.190 --> 00:34:31.840
Kneel!

00:34:37.480 --> 00:34:38.070
Qingyi.

00:34:49.550 --> 00:34:50.550
You unfilial son.

00:34:51.760 --> 00:34:52.760
I don't care about

00:34:53.760 --> 00:34:56.150
What and how many shady things

00:34:56.400 --> 00:34:57.360
You do outside.

00:34:59.400 --> 00:35:00.460
But bringing those

00:35:00.760 --> 00:35:02.220
Filthy and sketchy things

00:35:02.400 --> 00:35:04.480
Into the ancestral hall? Unfilial!

00:35:05.230 --> 00:35:06.290
Your incompetence

00:35:06.510 --> 00:35:08.440
Giving others leverage is unwise!

00:35:09.030 --> 00:35:10.230
Resorting to threats

00:35:10.480 --> 00:35:11.880
To chase Huo Minxian away

00:35:12.070 --> 00:35:14.070
Invalidates your stance, be it justified or not!

00:35:14.070 --> 00:35:15.280
How did I give birth to

00:35:15.280 --> 00:35:16.360
Such a bastard?

00:35:19.760 --> 00:35:21.420
Everyone walks alone in life.

00:35:21.590 --> 00:35:22.590
Don't let others

00:35:22.760 --> 00:35:23.820
Drain your energy.

00:35:24.230 --> 00:35:25.290
I don't deserve...

00:35:27.190 --> 00:35:28.920
Anything good, either.

00:35:29.230 --> 00:35:31.030
Qingyu, you're noble and upright,

00:35:31.030 --> 00:35:33.190
And Sister-in-Law, you're considerate,

00:35:33.190 --> 00:35:34.150
Unlike me,

00:35:34.760 --> 00:35:36.420
Who crawled out of the gutter.

00:35:37.150 --> 00:35:39.070
A vicious woman like Huo Minxian

00:35:39.320 --> 00:35:40.450
Is my perfect match.

00:35:49.110 --> 00:35:50.840
Even Huo Minxian knows that you

00:35:51.150 --> 00:35:52.320
Can't expect a son,

00:35:52.320 --> 00:35:53.440
Whom you birthed

00:35:53.440 --> 00:35:55.230
But didn't raise, to turn out perfect.

00:35:55.230 --> 00:35:56.960
Get your head out of the clouds.

00:35:56.960 --> 00:35:57.510
You...

00:36:00.260 --> 00:36:01.430
♪ Must it take heartache ♪

00:36:01.460 --> 00:36:03.320
♪ To know my heart belongs to you? ♪

00:36:04.010 --> 00:36:06.230
♪ Hearts cold no more ♪

00:36:06.330 --> 00:36:07.880
♪ Is every sweet dream ♪

00:36:08.000 --> 00:36:09.950
♪ Destined to fade away? ♪

00:36:10.700 --> 00:36:12.880
♪ Don't let it end in smoke ♪

00:36:13.020 --> 00:36:14.420
♪ Love and hate ♪

00:36:14.720 --> 00:36:16.030
♪ Till the very end ♪

